<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.5">
<l>āmaiyiṉmutu kattiṭaikkuti koṇṭutūmalar cāṭipōy</l>
<l>tīmaiceytiḷa vāḷaikaḷviḷai yāṭunīrttiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>nēmicērtaṭaṅ kaiyiṉāṉaini ṉaippilāvali neñcuṭai</l>
<l>pūmipāraṅka ḷuṇṇuñcōṟṟiṉai vāṅkipullaiti ṇimiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr with waters where play</l>
<l rend="indent">the young Vāḷai fish who engage in mischief,</l>
<l>going about, leaping on the backs of tortoises,</l>
<l rend="indent">bending white flowers to and fro,</l>
<l>[there are those who are a] burden to the earth,</l>
<l>having a hard heart, never thinking of him</l>
<l rend="indent">with the broad, discus laden hand – </l>
<l>remove the food [they are] eating</l>
<l rend="indent">and stuff grass [in their mouths instead]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
